description: Deletes a specified approval rule template. Deleting a template does not remove approval rules on pull requests already created with the template.

parameters.name: approvalRuleTemplateName
parameters.description: The name of the approval rule template to delete.

nested_items.name: approvalRuleTemplateId
nested_items.description: The system-generated ID of the deleted approval rule template. If the template has been previously deleted, the only response is a 200 OK.
